# Button

**Figma:** [Button](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=128-10284&p=f&m=dev)

Structure, variants, states, and token mappings below are derived from Figma node 128:10284.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Primary fill | `--bg-brand-default` |
| Primary text/icons | `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Outlined border/text | `--border-brand-default`, `--text-brand-default` |
| Subtle/selected fill | `--bg-brand-tertiary` |
| Disabled fill | `--bg-base-tertiary` |
| Disabled text | `--text-disabled-default` |
| Disabled border | `--border-base-default` |
| Secondary surface | `--bg-base-default` |

---

## Structure

- **Content:** Icon (optional, left) + Text (optional). Icon always left of text when both present.
- **Gap:** Space/100–200 between icon and text.
- **Shape:** Rounded corners; Radius/200 (8px) or Radius/Full (pill).
- **Rule:** Keep borders off by default for filled buttons.

---

## Variants (from Figma)

### Content variants (8)
1. Filled Icon only
2. Filled Text only
3. Outlined Icon only
4. Outlined Text only
5. Filled Icon + Text (filled icon)
6. Filled Icon + Text (outlined icon)
7. Outlined Icon + Text (filled icon)
8. Outlined Icon + Text (outlined icon)

### Theme variants
- **Primary Teal (Filled):** `--bg-brand-default` bg, `--text-brand-on-brand` text/icons. No border.
- **Primary Teal (Outlined):** `--border-brand-default` border, `--text-brand-default` text/icons, transparent bg.
- **Secondary Teal:** Same as primary; filled uses `--bg-brand-default` on hover.
- **Subtle/Light:** Filled `--bg-brand-tertiary`; outlined `--border-brand-default` border, `--text-brand-default` text/icons.
- **Prominent/Dark:** Darker filled; use only if defined in Figma.

---

## Sizes

| Size | Min height | Padding | Use |
|------|------------|---------|-----|
| Small | 32px | Space/100–200 | Desktop only |
| Medium | 40px | Space/200–400 | Default |
| Large | 48px | Space/400–600 | Prominent CTAs |

**Rule:** Avoid Small (32px) for touch devices; use ≥40px.

---

## States

| State | Filled | Outlined |
|-------|--------|----------|
| Normal | Base colors per theme | Base colors per theme |
| Hover | `--bg-brand-tertiary` | Darker `--border-brand-default` |
| Focus | Focus ring `--border-brand-default` | Focus ring `--border-brand-default` |
| Active | More pronounced than hover | More pronounced than hover |
| Disabled | `--bg-base-tertiary` bg, `--text-disabled-default` text. No hover/active. | `--border-base-default` border, `--bg-base-default` bg, `--text-disabled-default` text. No hover/active. |

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Tailwind: `bg-[var(--bg-brand-default)]`, `text-[var(--text-brand-on-brand)]`.
- Focus: `focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--border-brand-default)] focus:ring-offset-2`.
- Disabled: `disabled:opacity-60 disabled:cursor-not-allowed` or equivalent.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 128:10284.
